title: Trendster 5/12: Jeff Goldblum, Another 3, Bryan Adams, Tony Hawk
itunes:title: Trendster 5/12: Jeff Goldblum, Another 3, Bryan Adams, Tony Hawk
description:
On this edition of Trendster Jack and Miles discuss a viral fight video starring to people who look like Jeff Goldblum and Joe Exotic's ex-husband Joe, the Shelter in Place rule in LA has been extended 3 months, Bryan Adams tweeted some dumb shit, and Tony Hawk's Pro Skater 1+2 are being remastered!
